name: Patience Gothic Victorian Fairy Tattoo Flash
description:
Patience Gothic Victorian Fairy by Myka Jelina
Tattoo Design for personal use.
 © Myka Jelina

In your download you'll receive a full 8x10 color reference, one black and white 8x10 line drawing for easy transfer of the image by your tattoo artist, and a letter of authenticity to verify the image came directly from Myka.

You will be sent an email within 24 hours containing your new flash. Just print and head to your tattoo shop ;)
